---
import TodoList from "./TodoList.astro";
---

<div class="sidebar flex-col">
    <center>
        <div class="divider">************</div>
    </center>
    <div class="about-me">
        <h3>* About Me *</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><b>장래희망:</b> 익룡</li>
            <li><b>최애음식:</b> 국</li>
            <li><b>종교:</b> CEO Mindset</li>
            <li><b>싫어하는 것:</b>too many legs</li>
            <li><b>song:</b> ♪Free Bird by Lynyrd Skynrd♪</li>
            <li>
                <b>취미:</b> mindlessly surfing the internet for a quick dopamine
                boost and gathering useless information that takes up too much space
                in my brain and comtemplate about the meaning of life and our existance
                until I feel empty again
            </li>
            <li><b>최애음식2:</b> 크림빵</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="logos">
        <a href="/rss.xml"
            ><i class="fa-solid fa-square-rss"></i></a
        >
        <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3252360/Unemployment_Simulator_2018/"
            ><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i></a
        >
        <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1443200/Class_of_09/"
            ><i class="fa-brands fa-square-instagram"></i></a
        >
    </div>

    <TodoList />

    <style>
        .sidebar {
            background-color: #ffe4e8;
        }

        .logos {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border: pink 3px dotted;
            padding: 5px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: circle;
            padding-inline-start: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .profile-pic {
            border: pink 4px dotted;
        }

        .divider {
            padding: 10px 0px;
            color: rgb(255, 112, 255);
        }

        .about-me {
            text-align: center;
            color: cadetblue;
            text-shadow: pink 0 1px;
            border: pink 5px dotted;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 200;
            line-height: 1.4;

            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .about-me li {
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .about-me b {
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .sidebar {
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .logos a {
            color: tomato;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</div>
